Rion/Swyft

Rion spun on his heel, gladly following Diana away from the thing with 
teeth. He looked back, hoping that it wasn't following them. When he turned 
to look at Diana, however, she wasn't there!

"Diana?!"

Rion nearly jumped out of his armor as Diana proceeded to taunt the 
extremely large monster. What was she thinking?!

"What are you thinking?!"

Rion grabbed her wrist and tried dragging her away from the creature and 
toward the trees. Something told him they'd be safe there.

*****

Swyft:

Swyft shook the last of the water from her feathers, shaking her head 
vigoriously as she tried to get the water out of her ears.

"So, DevilDuer was it? Who's the leader of this faction anyway?"
